'''Dr. James''' is a neurosurgeon at [[St. Ambrose Hospital]].

==History==
When Dell passed out in the waiting room, Dr. James was called in. He diagnosed a brain bleed and drilled burr holes to relieve the pressure. When Dell's condition got worse, Charlotte insisted on another neurosurgeon because James had missed the problem the first time.

==Career==
He is a neurosurgeon at [[St. Ambrose Hospital]].
